{"tid":2025599,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"138假建築師《星島》登廣告撐警","createTime":"2020-05-20T10:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T12:04:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf3f90c668b180a70eb2be51d6c8001598119dc","tid":2025599,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:57:28.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200520/LQMORSOKS4DQMZ7MD6NOT5PRFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FLQMORSOKS4DQMZ7MD6NOT5PRFE%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=7349f5bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FLQMORSOKS4DQMZ7MD6NOT5PRFE%2F&h=4a981926\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200520/LQMORSOKS4DQMZ7MD6NOT5PRFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n138假建築師《星島》登廣告撐警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200520/large/1589906388_7c1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200520%2Flarge%2F1589906388_7c1a.jpg&h=cdf3b822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《星島日報》去年9月刊出一份題為「一群愛護香港的專業人士的聲明」的聯署聲明，多名建築、測量及工程建造界人士聯署批評反送中運動，惟今被揭至少名單中138人有偽冒身份之嫌。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年反修例運動期間，數百人以「建築師」、「測量師」等名義在《星島日報》聯署批評運動。建築師註冊管理局昨向會員發信稱，該份聯署中有138個「建築師」不在註冊名單，涉違《建築師註冊條例》第31條，曾去信《星島》希望提供廣告發起人資料惟未獲回應，該局於本月8日和13日報警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註冊管理局報警<br />\n<br />\n多名建築、測量及工程建造界人士於去年9月30日，以「一群愛護香港的專業人士的聲明」為題在《星島日報》發表聯署聲明，表示香港法治核心價值面臨前所未有的破壞及衝擊。當時其中一名疑「被聯署」的建築師鄭振揚已向建築師註冊管理局舉報，表示從未參與聯署，質疑有人冒認其身份簽署。<br />\n<br />\n建築師註冊管理局昨日向會員發信稱，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n惟未獲回應，遂於本月8日和13日分別透過電郵和電子報案室向警方舉報。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例第408章《建築師註冊條例》第31條，「不是名列註冊紀錄冊，但卻表示或在廣告中宣稱他自己是註冊建築師，或知情而容許別人表示或在廣告中宣稱他自己是註冊建築師」，即屬犯罪，可處罰款50,000元及監禁一年。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王春怡"},{"pid":"2244617ce05959f494ef611b4cb9d0b0499f4dec","tid":2025599,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"有巴打整合咗有咩可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次投標總共有7間，有3間係PR界既算係唔少野！<br />\n<br />\n我整合左Edelman, MSL, RedHill既Facebook同Twitter。<br />\nRedHill真係搵唔到Twitter<br />\n<br />\n個人意見<br />\n我有睇過呢幾間既Background，佢地既客都唔係細公司。<br />\nMSL好似有幫沙特做PR，沙特有好多負面野都係佢地去洗白<br />\n<br />\n我只是希望多啲人幫手打國際線<br />\n暫時咁多線黎講，條條線都好緊要<br />\n<br />\n幫手打下Twitter 戰線<br />\n多你一個真係好撚多！<br />\n<br />\nEdelman<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-hk.facebook.com/edelman/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-hk.facebook.com%2Fedelman%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=08c93e47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-hk.facebook.com/edelman/</a><br />\nTwitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EdelmanPR?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEdelmanPR%3Fs%3D20&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=84c2ed79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EdelmanPR?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMSL<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MSLGROUP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMSLGROUP&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=e1c03e8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MSLGROUP</a><br />\nTwitter<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/msl_group\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmsl_group&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=404bdd4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/msl_group</a> <br />\n<br />\nRedHill<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/redhillHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FredhillHQ%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=7b510f32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/redhillHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\nCredit